726647f-a.text:
Flushing Meadow Park (World 's Fair Site), A set of two views.

View No. 1 shows the Flushing Meadows looking north from Horace harding Blvd., showing at the left is 111th Street from Corona Avenue.

View number two is taken from a point west of 111th Street and Forty-seventh Avenue, and shows in the foreground Forty-seventh Avenue. The homes seen in this view are on the east side of 111th Street just north of the avenue. All buildings and the dumps have been leveled and the area is now a part of tNe World's Fair Grounds.

May 1923.
Views 1 and 2

Phigene L. Armbruster
